<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/532357-are-there-any-books-written-years-later">Are there any books written years later about the people that lived after the bomb was dropped?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_532357'><a id="like_count_community_question_532357" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/532357?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F27323.Hiroshima">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/532357-are-there-any-books-written-years-later">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/532357-are-there-any-books-written-years-later">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

